      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nFIS return file results matched back to submitted batch records. **Click any tile** to filter the detail. Sourced from `reporting.fact_reconciliation`.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Result Code | `fact_reconciliation.fis_result_code` | `000`=success \u00b7 other=rejection |\n| Result Message | `fact_reconciliation.fis_result_message` | Human-readable FIS response |\n| Status | `fact_reconciliation.reconciliation_status` | MATCHED=accepted \u00b7 UNMATCHED=rejected |\n| Reconciled Date | `fact_reconciliation.reconciled_at` | When Stage 7 processed the FIS return file |\n\n> **MATCHED** = FIS assigned FIS Person ID, CUID, and Card ID to the member.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
